The layers included in this web service are: Annual mean daily precipitation for the contiguous United States. Annual mean daily precipitation for Alaska. Annual mean daily precipitation for Hawaii. Mean daily precipitation for the contiguous United States for the month of January. Mean daily precipitation for the contiguous United States for the month of July. Mean daily precipitation in Alaska for the month of January. Mean daily precipitation in Alaska for the month of July. Mean daily precipitation in Hawaii for the month of January. Mean daily precipitation in Hawaii for the month of July. For more information about this dataset please visit the National Climatic Data Centers website at <a href="http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/ncdc.html">http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/ncdc.html</a></idAbs> <searchKeys> <keyword>precipitation Hawaii U.S. Alaska</keyword> </searchKeys> <idPurp>Mean Daily Precipitation for the Contiguous U.S., Alaska, and Hawaii. </idPurp> <idCredit>National Climatic Data Center</idCredit> <resConst> <Consts> <useLimit/> </Consts> </resConst> <idCitation> <resTitle>Mean Daily Precipitation for the U.S.</resTitle> </idCitation> </dataIdInfo> <Binary> <Thumbnail> <Data EsriPropertyType="PictureX"></Data> </Thumbnail> </Binary> </metadata>
